169
00:06:59.280 --> 00:07:01.040
misconception in neuroforensics.

170
00:07:01.040 --> 00:07:02.960
The short answer is absolutely not.

171
00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:03.520
Wait, really?

172
00:07:03.520 --> 00:07:04.800
Even if there is a massive tumor

