00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:06.640
right where their decision-making happens?

174
00:07:06.640 --> 00:07:07.200
Even then.

175
00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:10.240
A structural abnormality can support

176
00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:12.480
a claim like it can corroborate

177
00:07:12.480 --> 00:07:14.080
a history of erratic behavior,

178
00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:17.040
but it cannot automatically prove intent.

179
00:07:17.600 --> 00:07:19.040
Because having a compromised brain

180
00:07:19.040 --> 00:07:20.000
doesn't mean you didn't know

181
00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:20.960
