182
00:07:20.960 --> 00:07:22.160
in that specific moment.

183
00:07:22.160 --> 00:07:23.120
Precisely.

184
00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:24.240
The question isn't,

185
00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:25.520
is the scan real?

186
00:07:26.080 --> 00:07:28.480
It's what legal inference

