00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:31.280
is actually justified by this image.

188
00:07:31.280 --> 00:07:32.480
And the science just cannot

189
00:07:32.480 --> 00:07:34.000
make that leap on its own.

190
00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:34.640
Section, pause.

191
00:07:35.440 --> 00:07:36.800
So the physical brain structure

